<script>
import DatePicker from "vue3-persian-datepicker";
import "vue3-persian-datepicker/dist/datepicker.min.css";
import {
    reactive
} from "@vue/reactivity";

export default {
    name: "CustomHijriDatePicker",
    setup() {
        const state = reactive({
            date: "",
        });

        return {
            DatePicker,
            state,
        };
    },
};
</script>

<template>
  <DatePicker v-model="state.date" />
</template>
